3
00:00:11,469 --> 00:00:12,554
Thank you.

4
00:00:15,557 --> 00:00:17,559
Please help out those in need.

5
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:20,603
Just a little help is all I ask.

6
00:00:23,982 --> 00:00:25,191
Merry Christmas!

7
00:00:25,275 --> 00:00:26,735
62 DAYS UNTIL ASTEROID COLLISION

8
00:00:26,818 --> 00:00:28,987
I hope you all have a good Christmas.

9
00:00:29,654 --> 00:00:30,655
Hello.

10
00:00:38,663 --> 00:00:40,373
There's not much time left now.

11
00:00:41,374 --> 00:00:42,459
Are you scared?

12
00:00:44,377 --> 00:00:45,462
Not really.

13
00:00:45,962 --> 00:00:48,631
Actually, I'm kinda looking forward to it.

14
00:00:49,257 --> 00:00:50,550
The asteroid?

15
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:52,427
Mmm. Bam in the sky.

16
00:00:52,510 --> 00:00:54,888
It's gonna look so cool, I bet.
Don't you think?

17
00:00:55,472 --> 00:00:56,806
I don't wanna miss that.

18
00:01:02,896 --> 00:01:04,022
Where's Ha-yul?

19
00:01:04,105 --> 00:01:06,983
Uh… she's still passed out.

20
00:01:17,368 --> 00:01:18,244
What's this?

21
00:01:18,328 --> 00:01:20,330
Are you sticking together
till the very end?

22
00:01:20,413 --> 00:01:21,831
Of course.

23
00:01:21,915 --> 00:01:24,167
The three of us are staying together,
no matter what.

24
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:27,712
Uh-huh. And once we're all wiped out,
we'll be with our friends again.

25
00:01:28,505 --> 00:01:30,256
-Noona.
-What's up?

26
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,550
What are we getting
for Christmas this year?

27
00:01:34,427 --> 00:01:36,763
Santa's still gonna come, isn't he?

28
00:01:38,431 --> 00:01:40,391
I think he's staying home this year.

29
00:01:45,772 --> 00:01:47,357
Aw, that's not true.

30
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,068
And even if Santa doesn't show,
Mrs. Claus will be around.

31
00:01:50,151 --> 00:01:53,238
She'll bring lots of gifts for you.
Hmm? You'll see.

32
00:02:13,216 --> 00:02:15,343
Why are you standing out here?

33
00:02:17,595 --> 00:02:18,972
It's freezing.

34
00:02:19,556 --> 00:02:20,765
Aren't you cold?

35
00:02:21,558 --> 00:02:24,978
Hey, we make a good pair, don't we?

36
00:02:36,364 --> 00:02:37,323
Honey.

37
00:02:46,207 --> 00:02:47,709
Min-ho wouldn't want this.

38
00:02:48,543 --> 00:02:50,170
Let's say our goodbyes.

